{"tid":248723,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"教琴分享音樂！！","createTime":"2017-05-18T19:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T10:33:19.000Z","uid":117709,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d6e1fd92290a130385c76850d41bb150827cc8a","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T19:05:12.000Z","msg":"小弟由中一偶然愛上鋼琴，就不自禁沉迷其中，最終考到ATCL演奏級啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\n岩岩畢業，想搵下愛鋼琴的巴絲，如果你地未搵到老師，可以俾個機會我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享我所感受到的音樂！！<br />\n<br />\n由於我教琴經濟尚淺，只有數年伴奏經驗，加上志在分享音樂，學費勁低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唯一條件係你要有琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁你對鋼琴的愛才可以一直延續下去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb230345e400c21fc9856b537afd4a5adbe0e9c","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T19:06:47.000Z","msg":"有興趣的巴打加我TG:TommyFF"},{"pid":"990fd3152a384f60e5fd919aaafb67b9ba634ea3","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc3e03d5ba3228a3d0217f10f83feee176ae96fc","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc68767f984e5d15e33e73e9e0849cbfca1ae762","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b2de405278a3b3c107921c85a40463c80f058e","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass