img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前考五級肥左<br />\n想學番<br />\n唔知點入手<br />\n重有SIGHT READING好廢, 可以點練?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> THX"},{"pid":"8845fe8ed760352e8ff36e5bec1a565da7ff97e1","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問嘢得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前考五級肥左<br />\n想學番<br />\n唔知點入手<br />\n重有SIGHT READING好廢, 可以點練?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> THX</blockquote><br />\n當然係練番你練過嘅5級歌，因為你練過，應該會有印象，重拾番個feel先！sight reading真係要彈得多（彈唔同嘅歌，不斷重複搵音嘅過程，就會愈來愈快，因為你搵熟左，二來就咁睇個形狀就彈到）搵幾首自己鍾意但未彈過嘅歌試下（流行歌啊、古典啊、動漫歌啊⋯）但千萬不要彈太難嘅曲！"},{"pid":"d4d2077306ff3f4adee7603750548438f4cbc464","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Nscw9XZhAU&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0b181ece\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU</a>"},{"pid":"5ed80ddb9c52918513c52f39fc58d494060ad39c","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:00:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mYvI4Nl3WUg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmYvI4Nl3WUg&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=86a1c446\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mYvI4Nl3WUg</a>"},{"pid":"47c93303351a0ec8533c5cda6ceaae3ec493e303","tid":248723,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:01:40.000Z","msg":"hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51532a90e8538c3842da38de81578e1423ae5a0","tid":248723,"uid":62326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:14:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/mYvI4Nl3WUg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmYvI4Nl3WUg&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=86a1c446\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mYvI4Nl3WUg</a></blockquote><br />\n呢首咪8級考試曲B3<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d861a341e11fd4a7aff3bb55bbfe7941ec2fd7","tid":248723,"uid":74009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:16:15.000Z","msg":"有冇咩方法練琴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進度極慢，冇進展<br />\n9月考5級<br />\n<br />\n利申:Atcl violin"},{"pid":"6356b227e3bc6f189ab994320e3e9cb143ad954a","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHiHi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa9960dc258c1e106ffdac333127a5625b2df72","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/mYvI4Nl3WUg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmYvI4Nl3WUg&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=86a1c446\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mYvI4Nl3WUg</a></blockquote><br />\n呢首咪8級考試曲B3<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來真係有人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> thx bro"},{"pid":"ded103035fae36a9308296377c5f1b919f1a0ab4","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:58:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇咩方法練琴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 進度極慢，冇進展<br />\n9月考5級<br />\n<br />\n利申:Atcl violin</blockquote><br />\n要了解番點解進度慢，你係：<br />\n1.有成日練琴，但睇譜慢、練唔上手（好難練熟），音色較差<br />\n2.唔多練琴（umm⋯呢個就無乜討論）"},{"pid":"e5a482a424aa99e50b5e140937b52e8cce03791d","tid":248723,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T19:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Nscw9XZhAU&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0b181ece\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU</a></blockquote><br />\n中間彈得有啲亂喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb08f03ad1d7af3b242496f95a071decf17afe1","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:01:57.000Z","msg":"練琴當然要先放慢，切勿貪快！！當首歌有5頁，放慢練左頭兩頁（or頭個幾部分），練熟左先練落去。咁樣易建立muscle memory,唔會記憶薄弱。（往往一次過練太多，根本無細心番意到樂句，好快咁飛過，最後好難練熟）"},{"pid":"96b74922e3c194516270a2d02aa157581457d1dd","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Nscw9XZhAU&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0b181ece\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU</a></blockquote><br />\n中間彈得有啲亂喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個位應該係5連音對6連音，所以聽上黎會咁"},{"pid":"f460ac3808defd219ce3ea494ef1864ce0fffd7a","tid":248723,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>練琴當然要先放慢，切勿貪快！！當首歌有5頁，放慢練左頭兩頁（or頭個幾部分），練熟左先練落去。咁樣易建立muscle memory,唔會記憶薄弱。（往往一次過練太多，根本無細心番意到樂句，好快咁飛過，最後好難練熟）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係學琴 學開bass 想問 <br />\n點先可以做得同時期睇樂譜加拍子<br />\n好似好傻只係玩緊 guitarhero咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原全係聽音 <br />\n但樂理上唔都唔知點解果個音 同點解果個chord<br />\n仲有一點係個樂章好難走落去<br />\n<br />\n雖然basic上識睇少少樂譜 但都仲係用格仔去記<br />\n唔可以轉換到個識別出來<br />\n再加上唔同調開始都唔同<br />\n<br />\n真心配服 彈琴可以同時間睇高音加底音樂譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f58ef27c0c56537c1e8400e8c9042bb339661a3","tid":248723,"uid":120801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:11:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>練琴當然要先放慢，切勿貪快！！當首歌有5頁，放慢練左頭兩頁（or頭個幾部分），練熟左先練落去。咁樣易建立muscle memory,唔會記憶薄弱。（往往一次過練太多，根本無細心番意到樂句，好快咁飛過，最後好難練熟）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係學琴 學開bass 想問 <br />\n點先可以做得同時期睇樂譜加拍子<br />\n好似好傻只係玩緊 guitarhero咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原全係聽音 <br />\n但樂理上唔知點解果個音 同點解果個chord<br />\n仲有一點係個樂章好難走落去<br />\n<br />\n雖然basic上識睇少少樂譜 <br />\n但都係用格仔去記<br />\n唔可以轉換到個音出黎（即係睇個譜就唱到出黎）<br />\n加上唔同調開始都唔同<br />\n<br />\n真心配服 彈琴可以同時間睇高音加底音樂譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry 打完先發覺好多錯字好難明 改返先"},{"pid":"a5d4e5fbe3337551c067d6e1c2e40a1c4194568f","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>練琴當然要先放慢，切勿貪快！！當首歌有5頁，放慢練左頭兩頁（or頭個幾部分），練熟左先練落去。咁樣易建立muscle memory,唔會記憶薄弱。（往往一次過練太多，根本無細心番意到樂句，好快咁飛過，最後好難練熟）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係學琴 學開bass 想問 <br />\n點先可以做得同時期睇樂譜加拍子<br />\n好似好傻只係玩緊 guitarhero咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原全係聽音 <br />\n但樂理上唔都唔知點解果個音 同點解果個chord<br />\n仲有一點係個樂章好難走落去<br />\n<br />\n雖然basic上識睇少少樂譜 但都仲係用格仔去記<br />\n唔可以轉換到個識別出來<br />\n再加上唔同調開始都唔同<br />\n<br />\n真心配服 彈琴可以同時間睇高音加底音樂譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我未拉過小提琴會覺得小提琴難，拉小提琴嘅會過鋼琴睇譜難！係因為大家都未真係試過，試左，練過，就會好快征服到！<br />\n睇譜呢，就真係要打好個底，初時搵譜嘅過程真係非常非常重要！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵得多，<span style=\"color: red;\">就認得個位</span>，再睇到個音符唔同形狀（上上落落好像波浪咁），好自然順住個形狀彈到"},{"pid":"594df39d860a9a8cc62d6b2ddd3fcd07c81eea14","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:15:50.000Z","msg":"咩都要由淺入深，淺嘅地方就係決定你去得幾深，打好個底（認到拍子，音，建立到初步嘅音樂感），到你彈深嘅就唔會咁多阻礙！"},{"pid":"344ff11da020d93109b7934e801fd93407b04638","tid":248723,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:18:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Nscw9XZhAU&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0b181ece\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU</a></blockquote><br />\n中間彈得有啲亂喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個位應該係5連音對6連音，所以聽上黎會咁</blockquote><br />\n係咩 同我印象中有啲差距 同埋我覺得佢係音響上有啲嘈<br />\n唔知關唔關pedal事 同埋點解簡呢個版本既chopin?"},{"pid":"b24aec150822f143b608e492425c935d33542466","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:21:06.000Z","msg":"都想分享下，聽多d歌真係好有幫助，不論流行曲、純音樂、中樂、交響樂⋯聽咩都好。因為聽歌（特別係流行曲/classical period嘅），練到你嘅拍子、節奏感，聽聽下好快知道個pattern(伴奏/旋律）；聽romantic/ 20th-century嘅就建立個feel,對樂句表達嘅技巧。<br />\n<br />\n更重要係聽到唔同時代嘅樂曲音色上嘅轉變，到你真係去彈都容易catch up到"},{"pid":"b07648335d1db6c79899e301544ef377537cae79","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T20:23:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Nscw9XZhAU&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=0b181ece\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Nscw9XZhAU</a></blockquote><br />\n中間彈得有啲亂喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個位應該係5連音對6連音，所以聽上黎會咁</blockquote><br />\n係咩 同我印象中有啲差距 同埋我覺得佢係音響上有啲嘈<br />\n唔知關唔關pedal事 同埋點解簡呢個版本既chopin?</blockquote><br />\n係到sorry先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我聽左頭幾段就無聽，就放左上黎😹😹個版本都真係舊左小小，收音都差d,但都有比較過，算係入得耳（錯音就包容下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"43b6ef06b9cd7a53b1553df8e8642eb2eb4743e1","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T21:11:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oa9cfqzKcms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Foa9cfqzKcms&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=66f28fbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oa9cfqzKcms</a>"},{"pid":"ce7c73a7109ab8e37138516d0f3d815364678f25","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:59:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IfOJCKN148M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIfOJCKN148M&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8f8fa293\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IfOJCKN148M</a>"},{"pid":"5ba8999e72d785ff3791feb28efae1710559a9a2","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:00:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BjGwIwmv-lY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBjGwIwmv-lY&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c1080e40\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BjGwIwmv-lY</a>"},{"pid":"c9872a8b5822dc938444b8faa782dd420e261c8b","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:03:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GRxofEmo3HA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FGRxofEmo3HA&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f5efe8fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/GRxofEmo3HA</a>"},{"pid":"93694ebc1eef97a3559615f23f96baf4029ff184","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:04:48.