,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:02:15.000Z","msg":"必聽2<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_jBLyIQvNf0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_jBLyIQvNf0&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6e9d4a9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_jBLyIQvNf0</a>"},{"pid":"9f73407dbcb9a913025bde43d583f640f498dc67","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:03:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8F1a3LoDJGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8F1a3LoDJGg&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=429d3016\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8F1a3LoDJGg</a>"},{"pid":"97ffff5e4f16253baae4a6d469181260d777c3d4","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T20:09:12.000Z","msg":"正到爆<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vHqtJH2f1Yk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvHqtJH2f1Yk&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=11653436\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vHqtJH2f1Yk</a>"},{"pid":"5233e64412582e498cff4b104cc28861d1d86f99","tid":248723,"uid":74009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"就大問題係睇譜同埋左手問題<br />\n睇開弦樂譜，而家完全膠水咁停步<br />\n仲有就係指法問題，可能都係同弦樂太唔同，好難應付咁多個音"},{"pid":"ed2d95bf2f3496df816c0120a01d316d3e820174","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就大問題係睇譜同埋左手問題<br />\n睇開弦樂譜，而家完全膠水咁停步<br />\n仲有就係指法問題，可能都係同弦樂太唔同，好難應付咁多個音</blockquote><br />\n咁應該初學左手嘅時候基礎打得唔穩。試下練番簡單嘅左手（1-2級），甚至彈左手只有middleC到下個八度範圍嘅歌！<br />\n1.認番清左手嘅音（即左手低音譜嘅位置）<br />\n2.彈簡單嘅歌，左右手可以協調，再加快試下（都係簡單嘅歌）<br />\n3.練c major scale,都係由慢至快（一定要對拍子機），練下轉位嘅動作！<br />\n4.開始試下難嘅歌，唔好急，分開左右手練好左先，再雙手！"},{"pid":"314c334e1cf056ffee7810b8cfd9683f579ef5a9","tid":248723,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T18:53:08.000Z","msg":"想學呢首要學幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n拉克曼尼洛夫 第三協奏曲<br />\n<br />\n利申：譜都沒識睇"},{"pid":"89b7a5a5e8828dd93247d1945445c5b3ccd67c9f","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T19:57:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想學呢首要學幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n拉克曼尼洛夫 第三協奏曲<br />\n<br />\n利申：譜都沒識睇</blockquote><br />\n巴打⋯如果每日都用16個鐘去練琴，不出4年就彈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5373d9fa227162c73a471d11910fcf7f437df8ed","tid":248723,"uid":117709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T19:58:24.000Z","msg":"Rachmaninoff Piano concerto no.3公認係難嘅=="},{"pid":"ea32427da06634605dedfbf1c1c6910c1dca0c86","tid":248723,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想學呢首要學幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n拉克曼尼洛夫 第三協奏曲<br />\n<br />\n利申：譜都沒識睇</blockquote><br />\n巴打⋯如果每日都用16個鐘去練琴，不出4年就彈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}